{"tid":1827814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我係黑警女朋友 你問我答","createTime":"2020-01-17T08:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T09:13:21.000Z","uid":53247,"like":7,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc0798fd9e6942e05f99c748f36bf0a53eb47ad","tid":1827814,"uid":53247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思呃左你地入黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係到同大家宣布所有冇左份工同留左案底既你地全部都要考黑警！<br />\n<br />\n根本我地就唔可以再比多一個白警走人  我地要用盡一切方法去抗衡黑警數目<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最終目標要白警或手足做一哥！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n台灣明明獨立左都有一班共黨係到爭做總統<br />\n我地一樣要用同樣方法去做<br />\n<br />\n加上出左事既手足考警察先係最好既方法 用都係用正苦錢出糧比手足 ot津貼都係我地啲稅黎 手足做警察有咩問題！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但希望做左警察既你地勿忘祝心 唔好因為錢同升職或洗腦影你地  如果唔係就大撚鑊 仲多左黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔知有案底做唔做到警察"},{"pid":"1f716a620e037bb162fd9301d9c333ce9aa05b58","tid":1827814,"uid":53247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"唔該幫我推撚到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d387af654741662bc4eab6e7efe8d231420f24","tid":1827814,"uid":303982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"希望有咁堅定嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e659015445b54b29adb3c2ea842bc5f4126ad7","tid":1827814,"uid":185022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"有案底考警察會加分"},{"pid":"847a866cd5706e7d7b01c13143ba5713d3423876","tid":1827814,"uid":759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"你都ON撚9<br />\n有案底去考閪呀"},{"pid":"fc0bf09680eb0d2fd42018d9a8e453401fe27131","tid":1827814,"uid":86283,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"標題撚見一個封一個 拉"},{"pid":"66bc72949654c70f57109119a5375ff0fe5a8b2b","tid":1827814,"uid":271516,"li